{{Lunisolar November}} 
'''November 29''' is the 29th day of month {{ill|November (Lunisolar)|ja|11月 (旧暦)|lt=November|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}  – the 11th month of the traditional {{ill|Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|ja|旧暦|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|11=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} . If the month is {{Nihongo|Small|小}}  then this is the last day; if {{Nihongo|Big|大}}  then it is the second-last day.<ref>https://web.archive.org/web/20250111081847/https://www.chinaknowledge.de/History/Terms/calendar.html</ref><ref>https://www.nippon.com/en/japan-glances/jg00122/the-japanese-calendar.html</ref> Its {{ill|Rokuyō|ja|六曜|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} is {{ill|Senbu|ja|先負|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}.
== Events ==
