* {{ill|Bunji|ja|文治|qq=|qq=draft}}  first year ({{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=|qq=draft}} {{ill|1185|ja|1185th year|qq=|qq=draft}} {{ill|December 22|ja|12月22日|qq=|qq=draft}} ) – The Kamakura Shogunate, under the pretext of pursuing {{ill|Minamoto no Yoshitsune|ja|源義経|qq=|qq=draft}} , obtained imperial authorization from {{ill|Emperor Go-Shirakawa|ja|Emperor Go-Shirakawa|lt=Go-Shirakawa Hōō|lt_ja=後白河法皇|qq=|qq=draft}}  to station {{ill|shugo|ja|守護|qq=|qq=draft}}  and {{ill|jitō|ja|地頭|qq=|qq=draft}}  throughout the provinces.
== Births ==
* {{ill|Tenmon (era)|ja|天文|qq=|qq=draft}} 15th year ({{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=|qq=draft}}  {{ill|1546|ja|1546|qq=|qq=draft}}  {{ill|December 22|ja|12月22日|qq=|qq=draft}} ) – {{ill|Kuroda Takahisa|ja|黒田孝高|qq=|qq=draft}} , a military commander († {{ill|1604|ja|1604|qq=|qq=draft}} ).
* {{ill|Meiji|ja|明治|1=Meiji era|qq=|qq=draft}} 3rd year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=|qq=draft}}  {{ill|1871|ja|1871|qq=|qq=draft}}  {{ill|January 19|ja|1月19日|qq=|qq=draft}} ) – {{ill|Koganei Kimiko|ja|小金井喜美子|qq=|qq=draft}} , a novelist, essayist, and younger sister of {{ill|Mori Ōgai|ja|森鷗外|qq=|qq=draft}}  († {{ill|1956|ja|1956|qq=|qq=draft}} ).

== Deaths ==
* {{ill|Bunkyū|ja|Hōreki|qq=|qq=draft}} 7th year ({{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=|qq=draft}}  {{ill|1758|ja|1758|qq=|qq=draft}}  {{ill|January 9|ja|1月9日|qq=|qq=draft}} ) – {{ill|Kurushima Yoshinobu|ja|久留島喜内|qq=|qq=draft}} , a wasan expert (* {{ill|1660|ja|1660|qq=|qq=draft}}  circa).

