{{afc comment|1=This article as with the other date articles is relatively limited in scope to Japan. Reviewing the translation of this is good and also adding content translated from Chinese and Korean wikipedias will also be good. Both wikipedias are also relatively centered around their own countries for their Lunisolar calendar dates[[User:Immanuelle|Immanuelle]] ([[User talk:Immanuelle|talk]]) 00:16, 28 April 2025 (UTC)}} {{Globalize|article|Japan|date=April 2025}} {{Expand Chinese|1=十一月廿九|topic=hist|date=April 2025}} {{Expand Korean|1=음력 11월 29일|topic=hist|date=April 2025}} {{Lunisolar November|qq=}} '''November 29''' is the 29th day of month {{ill|November (Lunisolar)|ja|11月 (旧暦)|lt=November (Shimotsuki)|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/November (Lunisolar)|qq=}} – the 11th month of the traditional {{ill|Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|ja|旧暦|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|11=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|qq=}} . If the month is {{Nihongo|Small|小|qq=}} then this is the last day; if {{Nihongo|Big|大|qq=}} then it is the second-last day.<ref>https://web.archive.org/web/20250111081847/https://www.chinaknowledge.de/History/Terms/calendar.html</ref><ref>https://www.nippon.com/en/japan-glances/jg00122/the-japanese-calendar.html</ref> Its {{ill|Rokuyō|ja|六曜|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Rokuyō|qq=}} is {{ill|Senbu|ja|先負|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Senbu|qq=}}. == Events == * {{ill|Tengen (Japan)|ja|天元 (日本)|lt=Tengen|lt_ja=天元|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Tengen (Japan)|qq=}} first year ({{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Julian calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Julian calendar|qq=}} {{ill|978|ja|978th year|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/978|qq=}} {{ill|December 31|ja|12月31日|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/December 31|qq=}} ) – Because the following year was struck by the misfortune of Yōgo, the era name was changed from {{ill|Jōgen (Japan)|ja|貞元 (日本)|lt=Jōgen|lt_ja=貞元|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Jōgen (Japan)|qq=}} to {{ill|era change|ja|改元|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/era change|qq=}} * {{ill|Bunji|ja|文治|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Bunji|qq=}} first year ({{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Julian calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Julian calendar|qq=}} {{ill|1185|ja|1185th year|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1185|qq=}} {{ill|December 22|ja|12月22日|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/December 22|qq=}} ) – The Kamakura Shogunate, under the pretext of pursuing {{ill|Minamoto no Yoshitsune|ja|源義経|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Minamoto no Yoshitsune|qq=}} , obtained imperial authorization from {{ill|Emperor Go-Shirakawa|ja|Emperor Go-Shirakawa|lt=Go-Shirakawa Hōō|lt_ja=後白河法皇|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Emperor Go-Shirakawa|qq=}} to station {{ill|shugo|ja|守護|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/shugo|qq=}} and {{ill|jitō|ja|地頭|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/jitō|qq=}} throughout the provinces. == Births == * {{ill|Tenmon (era)|ja|天文|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Tenmon (era)|qq=}} 15th year ({{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Julian calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Julian calendar|qq=}} {{ill|1546|ja|1546|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1546|qq=}} {{ill|December 22|ja|12月22日|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/December 22|qq=}} ) – {{ill|Kuroda Takahisa|ja|黒田孝高|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Kuroda Takahisa|qq=}} , a military commander († {{ill|1604|ja|1604|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1604|qq=}} ). * {{ill|Meiji|ja|明治|1=Meiji era|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Meiji|13=User:Immanuelle/Meiji era|qq=}} 3rd year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Gregorian calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Gregorian calendar|qq=}} {{ill|1871|ja|1871|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1871|qq=}} {{ill|January 19|ja|1月19日|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/January 19|qq=}} ) – {{ill|Koganei Kimiko|ja|小金井喜美子|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Koganei Kimiko|qq=}} , a novelist, essayist, and younger sister of {{ill|Mori Ōgai|ja|森鷗外|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Mori Ōgai|qq=}} († {{ill|1956|ja|1956|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1956|qq=}} ).
== Deaths == * {{ill|Bunkyū|ja|Hōreki|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Bunkyū|qq=}} 7th year ({{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Julian calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Julian calendar|qq=}} {{ill|1758|ja|1758|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1758|qq=}} {{ill|January 9|ja|1月9日|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/January 9|qq=}} ) – {{ill|Kurushima Yoshinobu|ja|久留島喜内|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Kurushima Yoshinobu|qq=}} , a wasan expert (* {{ill|1660|ja|1660|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1660|qq=}} circa).
