le|13=User:Immanuelle/Julian calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Julian calendar|qq=}} {{ill|978|ja|978年|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/978|qq=}} {{ill|December 31|ja|12月31日|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/December 31|qq=}} ) – Because the following year was struck by the misfortune of Yōgo, the era name was changed from {{ill|Jōgen (Japan)|ja|貞元 (日本)|lt=Jōgen|lt_ja=貞元|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Jōgen (Japan)|qq=}} to {{ill|era change|ja|改元|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/era change|qq=}} * {{ill|Bunji|ja|文治|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Bunji|qq=}} first year ({{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Julian calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Julian calendar|qq=}} {{ill|1185|ja|1185年|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1185|qq=}} {{ill|December 22|ja|12月22日|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/December 22|qq=}} ) – The Kamakura Shogunate, under the pretext of pursuing {{ill|Minamoto no Yoshitsune|ja|源義経|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Minamoto no Yoshitsune|qq=}} , obtained imperial authorization from {{ill|Emperor Go-Shirakawa|ja|Emperor Go-Shirakawa|lt=Go-Shirakawa Hōō|lt_ja=後白河法皇|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Emperor Go-Shirakawa|qq=}} to station {{ill|shugo|ja|守護|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/shugo|qq=}} and {{ill|jitō|ja|地頭|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/jitō|qq=}} throughout the provinces. == Births == * {{ill|Tenmon (era)|ja|天文|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Tenmon (era)|qq=}} 15th year ({{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Julian calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Julian calendar|qq=}} {{ill|1546|ja|1546|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1546|qq=}} {{ill|December 22|ja|12月22日|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/December 22|qq=}} ) – {{ill|Kuroda Takahisa|ja|黒田孝高|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Kuroda Takahisa|qq=}} , a military commander († {{ill|1604|ja|1604|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1604|qq=}} ). * {{ill|Meiji|ja|明治|1=Meiji era|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Meiji|13=User:Immanuelle/Meiji era|qq=}} 3rd year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Gregorian calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Gregorian calendar|qq=}} {{ill|1871|ja|1871|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1871|qq=}} {{ill|January 19|ja|1月19日|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/January 19|qq=}} ) – {{ill|Koganei Kimiko|ja|小金井喜美子|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Koganei Kimiko|qq=}} , a novelist, essayist, and younger sister of {{ill|Mori Ōgai|ja|森鷗外|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Mori Ōgai|qq=}} († {{ill|1956|ja|1956|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1956|qq=}} ).
== Deaths == * {{ill|Bunkyū|ja|Hōreki|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Bunkyū|qq=}} 7th year ({{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Julian calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Julian calendar|qq=}} {{ill|1758|ja|1758|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1758|qq=}} {{ill|January 9|ja|1月9日|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/January 9|qq=}} ) – {{ill|Kurushima Yoshinobu|ja|久留島喜内|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Kurushima Yoshinobu|qq=}} , a wasan expert (* {{ill|1660|ja|1660|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1660|qq=}} circa).
